ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Title: Cobra World Order Part Two
ComicInfo.Summary: Cobra World Order Part Two: Duke's thought-dead wife Claire is found alive and reunited with him. Outback goes on leave to meet Spirit's family. Hawk faces Blue Ninjas in Toronto. Snake Eyes proves himself in combat with Storm Shadow and Granny Demon. Firefly and his allies hold another audience with Fred 191. Destro and the Baroness visit Zartan.
